{"tid":2115484,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情惡化 十大屋苑周末10宗跌近三成","createTime":"2020-07-19T13:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T10:36:18.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7b241f7236a8311c162d250f6490cda5bc8534","tid":2115484,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"疫情惡化 十大屋苑周末10宗跌近三成<br />\n文章日期：2020年7月19日 19:20<br />\n<br />\n&quot;疫情持續惡化，政府加強防疫措施下，周末睇樓量大跌，影響二手成交量。中原地產統計，十大屋苑周末錄10宗成交，較上周末下跌4宗或28.6%，已連續8個周末保持雙位數成交。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示...現時買家主要受疫情影響減少睇樓覓盤活動，以致成交量下跌，並不是對樓市失去信心，料疫情過後成交量將會反彈。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1595157732454&amp;issue=20200719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1595157732454%26issue%3D20200719&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8ptHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=cb7d0f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1595157732454&amp;issue=20200719</a>"},{"pid":"ca9949fba2e85d8c975d052e355024c0a660f8b2","tid":2115484,"uid":243855,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"成交跌，價唔跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61505cbee1ae29cf3223b8a2f51d01a788e2fa40","tid":2115484,"uid":37688,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"又餓一段時間 之後報復性買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573bb995ca6b480cb06d5782d2812a1171a4b30c","tid":2115484,"uid":199670,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"唔係話fake news架咩連燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 地產狗點會講真話 實際肯定跌9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{